# Netbox QR Code Plugin

[Netbox] plugin for generate QR codes for objects: Device, Module, Cable,
Powerfeed, Powerpanel, Location 

This plugin depends on [qrcode] and [Pillow] python library

[Downloads]
[Downloads]
[Downloads]

